review: It was really fun and challenging. We did Death by Wine. We were on a girls weekend with five of us had a blast. The staff was was very kind and helpful.

room_title: Escape room "Death By Wine" by Locked Room Omaha in Omaha
review: My friends and I had a blast in the Death by Wine and Titanic rooms! I thought completing one room may make the others seem easier, but each room has unique clues and puzzles for a new challenge every time. The props in each room are great. I also liked the private booking aspect compared to other escape room facilities. I hope the rumors of a Halloween-themed room are true!
